caption:
HEALTHY CHEF BANANA 🍌 BREAD - This is my gluten free version from my latest Cookbook " The Healthy Chef PURELY DELICIOUS". It’s yummy on it’s own or topped with a little ricotta + honey. 
GLUTEN FREE BANANA BREAD - BY TERESA CUTTER
300 g (10 ½ oz) ripe banana,
smashed
3 free-range/organic eggs
60 g (2 fl oz) raw honey or organic
maple syrup
60 g (2 fl oz) extra virgin olive oil or macadamia nut oil
1 teaspoon vanilla extract
1 teaspoon ground cinnamon
½ teaspoon bicarbonate of soda (baking soda)
1 tablespoon lemon juice
280 g ( 9  3/4 oz) almond meal

PREHEAT your oven to 160°C (320°F).
COMBINE smashed banana, eggs, honey, oil, vanilla,
cinnamon, bicarbonate of soda and lemon juice (the lemon activates the bicarb).
ADD the almond meal and mix well.
LINE a loaf tin (10 1/2 cm wide and 26 cm long).
SPOON banana bread mixture into the tin.
BAKE for1 hour and enjoy.
